originalText.text: I am a first time patient, and from the phone call from Christina at the front desk and having her be the sweetest, to walking in and having Jason greet me with such compassion, I knew it was going to be a great day in the office. Nurse Julia was great and made sure I was comfortable and ready for my procedure. Fay is one of a kind. I have been to several practices before her but I truly found my match with her and will be returning. Her technique is just what I needed. She’s quite literally the best at what she does. Fay was so patient and compassionate during the dissolving process. She made it so much easier. Fay also filled my lips and I have never felt better about them. My lips are absolutely perfect now. Confidence is power. Fay and the team at Fayced showed me that it’s possible to have it again! Thank you so much xx

originalText.text: Nurse Fay is the best! So sweet, so personable and really takes the time to listen to your concerns. She is knowledgeable, patient and was assuring during my visit (which was the first, but will be returning)! I’m already loving my new jawline I can’t wait to see how it looks in the long run. Couldn’t be happier or recommend her more. Not to mention - her staff is so friendly and welcoming. Terrific experience!

originalText.text:
First timer at Fayced Aesthetics! From the moment you walk into the office, you’re welcomed with warmth. The team made you feel comfortable and at ease.  Fay was so knowledgeable, nice, and she took the time to consult with me beforehand. She was transparent about the needs for my desired outcome. Loved how real she was!
Fay did an amazing job on my lips! The experience was painless and she yielded natural results. I’m so happy to have gone to her! I’ll definitely be returning. Thank you, Fay!

originalText.text:
I just finished my series of three Morpheus8 with Julia and a half syringe lip filler with Fay. Every part of my experience at Fayced NYC has been wonderful! The whole staff is so knowledgeable, easy to talk to and incredibly kind! The Morpheus8 treatment itself can be a little spicy, but they do everything to make it as quick and painless as possible and the results are absolutely worth it!
I had some scheduling conflicts for my last treatment and the front desk was always so understanding and accommodating. Everytime I walk into Fayced NYC I am greeted by beautiful people who make me feel beautiful! Seriously lovely staff and  knowledgeable, honest and talented practitioners. I absolutely recommend Fayced NYC if you’re considering cosmetic procedures!

originalText.text:
Nurse Fay, Julia, and the entire team at Fayced Aesthetics are the epitome of a dream team. They are professional, genuine, and welcoming. Fay is exceptional in beauty aesthetics, and her warm nature creates a sense of trust.

I received a Morpheus8 treatment with Julia, and I am so happy with the improvements in my skin. Julia is so patient and kind. She took the time to understand my skin concerns and thoroughly explained each step during the treatment while making sure I was comfortable.

Fayced Aesthetics is a true gem, and I highly recommend visiting!
